# Core (Serva)

- Use **pnpm** for scripts and installs (`pnpm dev`, `pnpm lint`, `pnpm build`).
- Keep changes **minimal and on-task**: no unrelated refactors, no extra docs unless asked.
- **Never** put real secrets or `.env` values in rules, commits, or chat; reference env var names only.
- Before inventing a new pattern, **read nearby code** in the same feature folder and match style, imports, and types; but be critical and use best practices if possible by suggesting.
- If getting stuck on a problem for a while, try searching the web for latest information or solution, you may have outdated data.
- After substantive edits, run **`pnpm lint`** when practical.
- Repo orientation: see root **`AGENTS.md`**.

## Import conventions

- **`@serva/database`** — Prisma client (`prisma`), generated model types, `hashPassword` / `verifyPassword` (script-safe, no `server-only`).
- **`@serva/database/dal`** — DAL query functions (`server-only` in several modules).
- **`@serva/shared`** — shared types, constants, helper utilities, auth validation schemas (e.g. `LoginSchema`, `SignupSchema`).
- **`@serva/auth`** or **`@serva/auth/<module>`** — session, authorize, permissions, cookies, password helpers.
- **`@serva/serva-ui`** — import UI from the package root ([`libs/serva-ui/src/index.ts`](libs/serva-ui/src/index.ts)): primitives, Serva components under `components/serva/`, `cn`, `ICONS`, hooks, etc. **Exceptions:** **`@serva/serva-ui/globals.css`**; **RHF form helpers** `InputField` / `InputFieldV2` from **`@serva/serva-ui/components/form/input-field`** and **`.../input-field-v2`** (not in the barrel—avoids pulling `react-hook-form` into every barrel consumer and fixes Turbopack resolution).
- **`@/*`** — app-local paths inside each app's `src/`.

## Multi-app architecture

- **`apps/serva-hub`** (`serva-hub`) — main app (port 4100). `(admin)` route group = **tenant** admin.
- **`apps/auth-portal`** (`auth-portal`) — centralized auth portal (port 3100). Owns login, signup, password reset, company selection, invite flows.
- **`apps/serva-admin`** (`serva-admin`) — platform super-admin (port 5100). Global company/identity management for `isPlatformAdmin` users. Protected by `platformAdminGuard`.
- Consumer apps redirect to **`AUTH_URL`** for login/logout; cookies are shared via **`COOKIE_DOMAIN`** in production.
